
				<p>Pages with sub-navigation require that there's no space (padding or margin) under the <a href="../modules/page-titles.php">page title</a> or <a href="../modules/report-headers.php">report title</a>. Simply add the <code>no-sub-navigation</code> to the first row: <code>class="l-row no-sub-navigation"</code></p>
			